&lt;h1 id="humans-are-exceptional"&gt;Humans Are Exceptional&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oct 22 2021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Humans aren&amp;rsquo;t just a form of bacteria that overran the planet&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Three out of these four theories have an interesting pattern to them. With good explanations in epistemology, we&amp;rsquo;re saying conjectures and their refutations and error correction is how we improve knowledge. With genetic evolution, genetic mutations, variation and natural selection weed out the ones that didn&amp;rsquo;t work. Then there&amp;rsquo;s memetic evolution on top of that, where we have ideas and then criticism weeds out the ideas that don&amp;rsquo;t work.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>No Truth Can Be Justified</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/no-truth-can-be-justified/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 Oct 2021 14:48:29 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/no-truth-can-be-justified/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/no-truth-can-be-justified.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
