&lt;p&gt;Be skeptical of absolute certainty&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt; All knowledge is conjectural. It&amp;rsquo;s always being guessed. It&amp;rsquo;s our best understanding at any given time.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>